Class Sample

java.lang.Object
backend.Sample
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
SampleAverage, SampleModern
public class Sample
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Sample accommodates ancestry sample kit related data (instances) and methods. It is used as a superclass of SampleModern, SampleAncient and SampleAverage.
